name: Ho Hum Fork
description:
Introduction

2 rappels (20 feet and 65 feet), 4 downclimbs, a sketchy jump over a keeper, and short stemming section. The ascent up the Crack exit is a bonus and is much more taxing than the descent. Approximately 1 1/2 hour technical section. Hiking time over 3 hours.
